name: SATWordQuiz
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: word quiz
des: Invoking the skill will start up a multiple choice question for a common SAT word, where you will have to choose the correct definition for the provided word. There are around 400 words, taken from https://www.vocabulary.com/lists/23400 and https://www.vocabulary.com/lists/191545. More words will be added eventually once I find them/figure out a better way to get them into the right format. Answer with "one", "two", or "three" (couldn't get "a" "b" "c" to work)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
